### =============================================================
### AlAshmar API - Flow: Generate Monthly Report
### =============================================================
###
### This file walks through generating monthly reports for:
###   - A specific student
###   - A specific teacher
###   - A specific class (halaqa)
###   - Overall attendance (all students/teachers)
###   - Overall points
###
### Instructions:
###   1. Run Step 1 (Login) first and copy the token.
###   2. Replace the placeholder IDs with real IDs from your DB.
###   3. Set @reportMonth and @reportYear to the desired period.
###   4. Run each report request individually.
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107

# Update these variables with real values:
@authToken   = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@studentId   = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@teacherId   = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011
@classId     = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041
@semesterId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
@reportMonth = 3
@reportYear  = 2025

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 1 - Authenticate
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 1: Login
# Copy the returned "token" value into @authToken above.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 2 - Student Monthly Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 2a: Student monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2b: Student monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/monthly?month={{reportMonth}}&year={{reportYear}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2c: Student all-time aggregated reports for review
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/all?periodType=AllTime
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 3 - Teacher Monthly Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 3a: Teacher monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 3b: Teacher monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/monthly?month={{reportMonth}}&year={{reportYear}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 3c: Points given by teacher this month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/points?fromDate={{reportYear}}-{{reportMonth}}-01&toDate={{reportYear}}-{{reportMonth}}-31&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 3d: Students progress under teacher (this semester)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/students-progress?semesterId={{semesterId}}&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 4 - Class (Halaqa) Monthly Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 4a: Class monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 4b: Class monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/monthly?month={{reportMonth}}&year={{reportYear}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 4c: Class memorization summary for semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/memorization?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 4d: Class points summary for semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/points?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 5 - Attendance Monthly Report (whole academy)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 5a: Overall attendance monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 5b: Overall attendance monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance/monthly?month={{reportMonth}}&year={{reportYear}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 5c: Attendance summary for the month (date range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance/summary?fromDate={{reportYear}}-{{reportMonth}}-01&toDate={{reportYear}}-{{reportMonth}}-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 6 - Points Monthly Report (whole academy)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 6a: Overall points monthly report (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 6b: Overall points monthly report (specific month and year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/monthly?month={{reportMonth}}&year={{reportYear}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 6c: Points overview for this semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/overview?semesterId={{semesterId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 6d: Top students by points this semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/top-students?semesterId={{semesterId}}&top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 6e: Top teachers by points this semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/top-teachers?semesterId={{semesterId}}&top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 7 - Semester Overview (bonus - full semester summary)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 7a: Full semester overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 7b: Semester statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 7c: Top 10 students in semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-students?top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 7d: Top 10 teachers in semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/top-teachers?top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 7e: Class summaries in semester
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/semesters/{{semesterId}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
